# Kargino, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Kargino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 89 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Kargino is located 6&nbsp;km northwest of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Kabansk is the nearest rural locality.
